---
description: Development Practices and Guidelines
alwaysApply: true
---

Development practices when you build code:
1. Always run the linter for code quality static analysis in the respective `backend/` or `frontend/` projects directory: `pnpm run lint:fix` 
2. Always run the the type checker in the respective `backend/` or `frontend/` projects directory: `pnpm run typecheck`
3. Always run tests `pnpm run test` (in the respective `backend/` or `frontend/` projects directory)
4. Address any issues that arise from the above to complete your coding cycle